Description: PiTilt monitoring service
 A Python application packaged with a self-contained virtualenv. The
 application code is installed under /opt/pitilt, all Python dependencies
 from requirements.txt are bundled into /opt/pitilt/venv, configuration
 lives in /etc/pitilt and the program runs as a systemd service under a
 dedicated unprivileged "pitilt" user.
